Hollie Thursday evne.

Tho. Oookrill being baylyf to the ebbot did meete by sonu Rise the Oenieres, the Strangwayes, the Eldringtones, and Allettson‚ who weere bound to this service, in the Strye—head

hard by Lyttell-beck‚ and the said (lockrill did see every one cutt downe with aknyie, he appoynting the wood, so mucheas should serve.
